      "enGB": "Arcane Metamastery — Extend",
      "enGB": "Arcane Metamastery — Flaring",
      "enGB": "You can apply a metamagic feat with Arcane Metamastery that increases the slot level of the spell by up to 4 levels instead of 2.",
