      "enGB": "Bounty Hunter adds <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Stealth\">Stealth</link></color></b> to the list of her class <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Skills\">skills</link></color></b>. She also becomes proficient with light armor, clubs, light maces and heavy maces.\nIf the character already has the class skill, <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Weapon_Proficiency\">weapon proficiency</link></color></b> or armor proficiency granted by the selected background from her class during character creation, then the corresponding <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Bonus\">bonuses</link></color></b> from background change to a +1 trait bonus in case of skills, a +1 trait bonus in case of weapon proficiency and a –1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Check_Penalty\">Armor Check Penalty</link></color></b> reduction in case of armor proficiency.",
      "enGB": "Chelaxian Diabolist adds <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Knowledge_Arcana\">Knowledge (arcana)</link></color></b> to the list of her class <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Skills\">skills</link></color></b>. She also gains a +4 dodge <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Bonus\">bonus</link></color></b> to <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Class\">AC</link></color></b> against devils.\nIf the character already has the class skill, <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Weapon_Proficiency\">weapon proficiency</link></color></b> or armor proficiency granted by the selected background from her class during character creation, then the corresponding bonuses from background change to a +1 trait bonus in case of skills, a +1 trait bonus in case of weapon proficiency and a –1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Check_Penalty\">Armor Check Penalty</link></color></b> reduction in case of armor proficiency.",
