      "enGB": "Shackles Corsair adds <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Mobility\">Mobility</link></color></b> and <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Athletics\">Athletics</link></color></b> to the list of her class <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Skills\">skills</link></color></b>. She also becomes proficient with scimitars. In addition Shackles Corsair gains a +2 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Bonus\">bonus</link></color></b> to <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:CMD\">CMD</link></color></b> against trip attempts.\nIf the character already has the class skill, <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Weapon_Proficiency\">weapon proficiency</link></color></b> or armor proficiency granted by the selected background from her class during character creation, then the corresponding bonuses from background change to a +1 trait bonus in case of skills, a +1 trait bonus in case of weapon proficiency and a –1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Check_Penalty\">Armor Check Penalty</link></color></b> reduction in case of armor proficiency.",
      "enGB": "Smith adds <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Athletics\">Athletics</link></color></b> to the list of her class <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Skills\">skills</link></color></b>. She also becomes proficient with light hammers and warhammers, and gets a +1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Bonus\">bonus</link></color></b> on <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw\">Fortitude saving throws</link></color></b>.\nIf the character already has the class skill, <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Weapon_Proficiency\">weapon proficiency</link></color></b> or armor proficiency granted by the selected background from her class during character creation, then the corresponding bonuses from background change to a +1 trait bonus in case of skills, a +1 trait bonus in case of weapon proficiency and a –1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Check_Penalty\">Armor Check Penalty</link></color></b> reduction in case of armor proficiency.",
      "enGB": "Ustalavic Peasant adds <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Athletics\">Athletics</link></color></b> to the list of her class <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Skills\">skills</link></color></b>. She also becomes proficient with scythes. In addition Ustalavic Peasant gains a +1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Bonus\">bonus</link></color></b> to <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Class\">AC</link></color></b> and <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Damage\">damage</link></color></b> while under fear effects.\nIf the character already has the class skill, <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Weapon_Proficiency\">weapon proficiency</link></color></b> or armor proficiency granted by the selected background from her class during character creation, then the corresponding bonuses from background change to a +1 trait bonus in case of skills, a +1 trait bonus in case of weapon proficiency and a –1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Check_Penalty\">Armor Check Penalty</link></color></b> reduction in case of armor proficiency.",
      "enGB": "Varisian Explorer adds <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Trickery\">Trickery</link></color></b> and <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Knowledge_World\">Knowledge (world)</link></color></b> to the list of her class <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Skills\">skills</link></color></b>. She also gains a +1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Bonus\">bonus</link></color></b> on <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Saving_Throw\">Reflex saving throws</link></color></b>.\nIf the character already has the class skill, <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Weapon_Proficiency\">weapon proficiency</link></color></b> or armor proficiency granted by the selected background from her class during character creation, then the corresponding bonuses from background change to a +1 trait bonus in case of skills, a +1 trait bonus in case of weapon proficiency and a –1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Check_Penalty\">Armor Check Penalty</link></color></b> reduction in case of armor proficiency.",
      "enGB": "Warrior of the Linnorm Kings adds <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Mobility\">Mobility</link></color></b> to the list of her class <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Skills\">skills</link></color></b>. She also becomes proficient with handaxes, battleaxes and greataxes. In addition Warrior of the Linnorm Kings gains 5 cold <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Energy_Resistance\">resistance</link></color></b>.\nIf the character already has the class skill, <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Weapon_Proficiency\">weapon proficiency</link></color></b> or armor proficiency granted by the selected background from her class during character creation, then the corresponding <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Bonus\">bonuses</link></color></b> from background change to a +1 trait bonus in case of skills, a +1 trait bonus in case of weapon proficiency and a –1 <b><color=#703565><link=\"Encyclopedia:Armor_Check_Penalty\">Armor Check Penalty</link></color></b> reduction in case of armor proficiency.",
