      "enGB": "Bewitching Reflex",
      "enGB": "A black blade has an arcane pool with a number of points equal to 1 + its Intelligence bonus.",
      "enGB": "Black Blade Arcane Pool",
      "enGB": "The Black Blade starts with the following stats:\nEgo: 5\nInt: 11\nWis: 7\nCha: 7",
      "enGB": "Black Blade Base Stats",
      "enGB": "A black blade's enhancement bonus increases as it gains levels. It is +1 at level 1 and increases by 1 every 4 levels thereafter. A black blade cannot be wielded by anyone other than its owner.",
      "enGB": "Black Blade",
      "enGB": "Your Black Blade takes the form of a Bastard Sword.",
