      "enGB": "Sorcerer",
      "enGB": "Arcanist",
      "enGB": "Dragonheir Scion Bloodline",
      "enGB": "Dwarves are both tough and wise, but also a bit gruff. They gain +2 Constitution, +2 Wisdom, and –2 Charisma.",
      "enGB": "Dwarf Ability Modifiers",
      "enGB": "The following alternate traits are available.",
      "enGB": "Alternate Traits",
      "enGB": "No Alternate Trait",
      "enGB": "None",
      "enGB": "Some dwarves use their unwavering stubbornness to get what they want in negotiations and other business matters. They gain a +2 racial bonus on Persuasion checks and Persuasion is a class skill for them.\nThis racial trait replaces defensive training, hatred.",
      "enGB": "Stoic Negotiator",
      "enGB": "Not all dwarves are as standoffish and distrusting as their peers, though they can be seen as foolhardy and brash by their kin. Dwarves with this racial trait gain +2 Constitution, +2 Charisma, and -2 Intelligence.\nThis racial trait alters the dwarves’ ability score modifiers.",
      "enGB": "Stoutheart Dwarf",
      "enGB": "You become proficient with earth breakers and can use them as a weapon.",
      "enGB": "Weapon Proficiency (Earth Breaker)",
      "enGB": "1 round/5 levels",
      "enGB": "1 round/4 levels",
      "enGB": "Elder Flaming",
      "enGB": "Elder Incinerating",
      "enGB": "Elder Greater Corrosive",
      "enGB": "Elder Caustic",
      "enGB": "Elder Frost",
      "enGB": "Elder Freezing",
      "enGB": "Elder Shocking",
      "enGB": "Elder Greater Shocking",
      "enGB": "You are adept at breaching magical defenses and overcoming resistance to your magic.\nWhen attempting a caster level check to dispel an effect or overcome spell resistance roll twice and take the higher result.",
      "enGB": "Eldritch Breach",
      "enGB": "Eldritch Scion Bloodline",
