      "enGB": "Opposition Research — Transmutation",
      "enGB": "Whenever a creature fails a saving throw and takes fire damage from one of your spells, it catches on fire. This fire deals 1 point of fire damage per spell level at the beginning of the burning creature’s turn. The fire lasts for 1d4 rounds.",
      "enGB": "Freezing Spells Effect",
