      "enGB": "You bear intricate tattoos that inspire and empower your natural magic ability. These tattoos mark you as a worker of the ancient traditions of Varisian magic. A Varisian tattoo typically consists of a long string of complex characters from the Thassilonian alphabet.\nSelect a school of magic in which you have Spell Focus. Spells from this school are cast at +1 caster level.",
